le-plus-1" target="_blank" title="Cliquez pour partager sur Google+" id="sharing-google-2084"><span>Google</span></a></li><li class="share-email"><a rel="nofollow" class="share-email sd-button share-icon" href="http://carlchenet.com/2013/10/16/brebis-0-7-controle-automatise-de-vos-sauvegardes/?share=email" target="_blank" title="Cliquez pour envoyer par email à un ami"><span>Email</span></a></li><li class="share-end"></li></ul></div></div></div><div class='sharedaddy sd-block sd-like jetpack-likes-widget-wrapper jetpack-likes-widget-unloaded' id='like-post-wrapper-7722010-2084-53d049f989f71' data-src='//widgets.wp.com/likes/#blog_id=7722010&amp;post_id=2084&amp;origin=carlchenet.wordpress.com&amp;obj_id=7722010-2084-53d049f989f71' data-name='like-post-frame-7722010-2084-53d049f989f71'><h3 class='sd-title'>Like this:</h3><div class='likes-widget-placeholder post-likes-widget-placeholder' style='height:55px'><span class='button'><span>J&#039;aime</span></span> <span class="loading">chargement&hellip;</span></div><span class='sd-text-color'></span><a class='sd-link-color'></a></div></div>					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
			
	
			<footer class="entry-meta">
